NAME

	Acme::Lambda::Expr - Lambda expressions

SYNOPSIS

	use Lambda::Expr;

	my $f = $x + $y;
	print $f->(2, 3); # => 5

DESCRIPTION

	Acme::Lambda::Expr provides lambda expressions.

	See "perldoc Acme::Lambda::Expr" for the rest of the document.

DEPENDENCIES

	perl 5.8.1 or later.

INSTALLATION

	To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

